        <p>Based on your current narrative, your care team wants to ask a few more questions to better understand you.</p>
    </aside>
    <section class="w-3/4 h-screen min-h-full overflow-y-auto shadow-xl p-12 bg-white">
        <div class="min-h-full">
            <h2 class="text-black text-4xl">{{ question }}</h2>
